This paper deals with image composition and blending, which are tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The proposed method involves the use of a deep network to optimize the blending process, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
